</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/Fichier:Schwarzwald_1.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/66/Schwarzwald_1.jpg/180px-Schwarzwald_1.jpg" width="180" height="135" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/Fichier:Schwarzwald_1.jpg" class="internal" title="Agrandir"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
